{"tid":441759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩成半港女曾出軌 多過男士仲有30%話預出軌","createTime":"2017-10-20T03:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T04:11:12.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a116994d35ddaa12468642ba231116596fdf1a","tid":441759,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"風流」不再是男士專利！有約會平台調查發現，24％港女坦言曾出軌，大幅拋離亞洲其他地區，近30％人更謂未來會或有可能出軌；相較之下，男士僅18％人承認曾出軌。調查亦發現網上約會「中伏度」高，有女生曾遇中年禿頭漢以「舊相扮年輕」。<br />\n<br />\n約會平台esync今年8至9月訪問330名單身港人，了解他們戀愛態度，結果發現24％女性曾出軌，遠高於同類調查中新加坡、馬來西亞及泰國的8％至18％；10.4％及19.2％港女坦言將來會或有可能出軌。男士方面，僅18％人承認曾出軌，5.9％及20.9％人指將來會或有可能出軌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/兩成半港女曾出軌-多過男士-225051978.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90%E5%8D%8A%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%9B%BE%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C-%E5%A4%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB-225051978.html&d=mDttzsPH%2Bd2ORI6Ujl%2Bz8zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=52420cdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/兩成半港女曾出軌-多過男士-225051978.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司件新仔，同另外部門女同事入公司前已在大學拍拖，唔駛3個月條女已經俾已婚上司食了，但仍然被瞞住，直到其他同事傳開先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2931bb217a5ff4c0bc1001982aae2dfb9267d77","tid":441759,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"港女一向養唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0275a3d3d6d9468218f8829fdb542197f8742925","tid":441759,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d84738ed88a94f14f4671e2ed9ba120f26611a1","tid":441759,"uid":117365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span 